25:29.237 --> 25:30.693
Looks like winds
reached about 160.

25:30.780 --> 25:33.863
I can’t believe
I didn’t get any footage.
Damn it!

25:33.950 --> 25:35.531
Look, over there.

25:35.660 --> 25:37.821
It’s a rainbow.
All right.

25:37.954 --> 25:40.366
[Chattering ]
[ Booth ] You see this?
You see all this destruction?

25:40.456 --> 25:43.289
You still think I’m being
overprotective? You know what?
You shouldn’t have come.

25:43.376 --> 25:45.662
I got a lot of valuable
information, Booth.

25:45.753 --> 25:49.871
Plus, it looks like
you’re the one who
shouldn’t have come.

25:49.966 --> 25:51.581
My car!

25:52.760 --> 25:54.842
- It’s my car.
- [ Toni ]
Check this out.

25:54.929 --> 25:57.762
Sweets! Hey, where you
goin’, Bones?

25:59.058 --> 26:01.390
Hold up.
Bones, wait.

26:01.477 --> 26:03.638
I need a ride.
I need a ride back.

26:09.944 --> 26:12.151
You thinking
of starting a band?

26:12.238 --> 26:14.229
[ Scoffs ]
