26:14.323 --> 26:18.282
Do you have any idea
how difficult it is for me
to tell my father anything?

26:18.369 --> 26:20.746
All I want is for him
to just see things...

26:23.321 --> 26:23.416
from my perspective, right,
so I can get some sleep here,

26:23.416 --> 26:25.577
but he just insists
that he knows everything,
and it’s just—

26:25.668 --> 26:27.784
Angela.

26:27.879 --> 26:31.667
- Didn’t someone
get murdered?
- Oh, yes. Yes.

26:31.758 --> 26:36.548
So, based on the presence
of certain particulates...

26:36.637 --> 26:38.343
and the absence of others,

26:38.431 --> 26:41.594
we know that the victim
was spit out from the tornado...

26:41.684 --> 26:45.597
somewhere within
this red area here.

26:45.688 --> 26:48.851
Meaning he was
picked up somewhere
in this lower section.

26:48.941 --> 26:50.806
That’s still
a lot of area to search.

26:50.902 --> 26:53.393
I know. That’s why I tried
to narrow it down further.

26:53.488 --> 26:57.322
I looked at the particulate
density ratios and used
the probability index,

26:57.408 --> 27:00.491
